Easy cute little desktop app tutorial.

Desktop applications like these. This is how to make your very first desktop application, super beginner friendly. I have a full step-by-step tutorial on my YouTube, from how to set up everything that you'll need to coding and styling your very first desktop app. Or if you just want to grab a template code. Bye <3
